snippet.title: How to Polish Amber at Home
snippet.description:
Good morning rock hounds!
This is the first video from my workshop so if you want to see more, or have topics you’d like videos on please leave me a comment and let me know. This is obviously the promised video on how to Polish all your beautiful Amber I have been shipping out over the past 2 weeks. 

The Amber is going to look very dark although you can do what I did and place it on a light table, you can also polish and/or oil it to be able to see those beautiful colors all the time!
